                        <h2 class="margin-top-lg">Ignition Interlock Requirements</h2>
                        <p>Most restored licenses require installation of an ignition interlock device:</p>

                        <ul class="list-styled-disk">
                            <li><strong>Breath test required</strong> before starting vehicle</li>
                            <li><strong>Rolling retests</strong> required while driving</li>
                            <li><strong>Monthly calibrations</strong> and data downloads required</li>
                            <li><strong>Violations</strong> can result in license re-revocation</li>
                            <li><strong>Costs</strong> include installation, monthly fees, and calibrations</li>
